PrecisAcceptance of a "DESIGNATION" sanctionned by the HAY RIVER BAND OF INDIANS whereby it surrenders some 11.13 hectares on HAY RIVER DENE INDIAN RESERVE NO. 1 in the Northwest Territories for a term of fifty (50) years, so that it can be leased for housing and cultural uses (Lots 125, 143 & 145).
